In fantasy.
Manga, Animate, Movies there is a subject of interest.
The work done in the subject of interest and what it express by logic and emotion. 
Will broaden the viewers perspective.

Those perspective might change the one behave or the understand of the subject and life.
Ultimately it carries a value, a value that seeded for a change in action.

Intellectual property is the combination of the work and ownership.
The work is the product of "intellect" the property is how we view the possession. 

For the future, property is a mirror of society standard in value.
Intellect is the property of the society. 
When ideas and knowledge freely transmit within the society, 
how we qualify the value of such possession is the most curcial indicate of the future.

